{
  "text": "A second interpretation arises from the concept of placement values [CITATION_1] . [CITATION_2] showed a connection between average placement values and the full AUC. We extend their result to the partial AUC here, as it provides an interesting interpretation of the partial AUC as well as a simpler estimator:",
  "correct_citation": {
